Name:White Werewolf
Desc:The White Werewolf wakes up with the rest of the werewolves and chooses a player to attack with them. The White Werewolf is not part of the werewolf team and seeks out to kill every other player in the entire game. Every second night, the White Werewolf wakes up and may attack another werewolf.
